## Performance Characteristics

### Current Performance (GTX 1050, 4GB VRAM)
- **FPS**: 40-50 FPS (main_gpu.py)
- **Detection Latency**: ~300ms (async, non-blocking)
- **Recognition Latency**: ~500ms (async, non-blocking)
- **GPU Memory**: ~2.5GB TensorFlow + ~1GB PyTorch
- **CPU Usage**: Moderate (threaded architecture)

### Optimization Strategies
- Detection runs every 10 frames (configurable)
- Recognition runs every 30 frames per track (configurable)
- GPU cache cleared every 100 frames
- Batch processing enabled for embeddings
- Mixed precision (FP16) for 2x speedup

